{"tid":1716902,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"黃金經濟圈 - 水門海南雞","createTime":"2019-11-13T12:55:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T16:33:38.000Z","uid":157907,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"653c002e630a2dcb9f905b0782f8c598f774d002","tid":1716902,"uid":157907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:55:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JkR5Uyb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJkR5Uyb.jpg&h=378440c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eXFKqES.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeXFKqES.jpg&h=725961f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水門同龍門或渣哥一樣，係出名既黃店，長時間都大量人幫襯<br />\n但水門同其餘兩間唔同，水門會利用自己既知名度，主動叫食客去附近既黃店，從而建立起一個區域既黃金經濟圈<br />\n<br />\n其實渣哥同龍門既食客都多不勝數，想懲罰佢地往往要排成個鐘，所以我建議比較出名既黃店呼籲食客分流去其他黃金，建立一個大黃金經濟圈"},{"pid":"07e0fe499788776bed5b8476456699b7c770d70d","tid":1716902,"uid":163943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:56:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dfbc4b9a1dcd57b725874be05ec619ef81817d44","tid":1716902,"uid":41850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:58:24.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ccf6f8dfb962ae54986b5b25a4a7c9938d62b3","tid":1716902,"uid":90025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:14:55.000Z","msg":"食過上環店<br />\n個飯真係好細 <br />\n推筲箕灣黃金雞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(但黃金雞可改善嘅係餐具唔好用福建製 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"131ca57585e0802d3f66bd3e3e18c09e4a9e7576","tid":1716902,"uid":205424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:35:33.000Z","msg":"同一層西九八樓既 89同喇沙專門店都要好好懲罰"},{"pid":"93887f4e3986085b0a6b03fa06da2d50a95feb86","tid":1716902,"uid":200538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:08:23.000Z","msg":"18區黃藍食店Bot<br />\n<a href